Summary: looks like a cloud till you zoom in.
divs: Sighting DetailsThe Blue Angels were putting on a show in Seattle. They allways seem to pass over my house, so I was trying to get some photos. I was playing around with my digital camera and added an IR lens filter. There were no clouds and it was sunny and clear. As I was taking a series of photos, I could see nothing. but as I was viewing the photos something showed up. Condensation maybe? no clouds and humidity was very low. you be the judge as I am reluctant to call it a ufo. i did try to duplicate the photo not five minuets later without success. Some of my friends say it could be the Goodyear blimp, but i should have seen it while I was taking the photo. others say I doctored it in photoshop. I did not in any way doctor the photo. Two photos are attached. The first one was just lightened a little.
